<item>
            <title>[LU-16488] Wrong help message for &apos;lctl interface_list&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16488</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
# lctl interface_list
You must run &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;interface_list &amp;lt;network&amp;gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt; command before &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;network&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But the right syntax is&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
lctl --net tcp0 interface_list&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
